<h2 id="goals">Goals</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Observe the effect of adding mixing various solutions or changing the temperature of a solution.</li>
  <li>Explain the observations using the relevant chemical reactions and Le Ch√¢telier‚Äôs principle.</li>
  <li>Be through!
    <ul>
      <li>Do not simply state ‚ÄúSodium hydroxide was added and the reaction shifted left.‚Äù</li>
      <li>See Figure 1 and 2 for some ideas</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

